{"data": {"post": {"main": "{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"md\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"text\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"WebAssembly Music is the concept of storing a full length track of music in a tiny file. Typically less than 50KB. Instead of the music being stored in a WAV or MP3, which is often several megabytes in size, we store the music in a `.wasm` file. A `.wasm` file is a program, with instructions to generate the audio.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nA demo of such music can be found at https://webassemblymusic.near.page/ which is fully stored on the NEAR blockchain.\\\\\\\"}"}, "index": {"post": "{\\\\\\\"key\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"main\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"value\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"md\\\\\\\"}}"}}, "handle": "webassemblymusic"}

{"handle": "tooling", "community_addon": {"id": "kp910a", "enabled": true, "addon_id": "wiki", "parameters": "{\\\\\\\"title\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Tooling Community / WG Calls\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"subtitle\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"**Welcome to the Tooling Community and Work Group Calls page, where you can find recaps and information on previous community and work group calls related to NEAR DevHub and tooling development.**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**Note: These formal calls are conducted to review specific proposals, discuss attestations, or vote on decisions**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n### [Community Call] #2: Jan 30th, 2024\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**MODERATOR :** Lyudmil\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**VIDEO :** [Tools Community Call #2 \\\\u{2013} NEAR DevHub January 30th, 2024](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I-u5WDLfWWU)\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**AGENDA**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n- LavaNetwork presents their solution that aims to help scale the RPC services demand - https://lava-etwork.xyz\\\\\\\\n- Vlad presents Cargo Near Template - https://github.com/near/cargo-near-ne...\\\\\\\\n- near-sdk-rs 5.0 soon to be released with ABI enabled by default.\\\\\\\\n- Noah shares heads-up on the simplified dev-container he is currently working on.\\\\\\\\n- NearBlocks is soon to release a version of the explorer on BOS - https://beta.nearblocks.io\\\\\\\\n- Andrey Talks about SourceScan - NEAR-native smart contract verifier https://near.org/sourcescan.near/widg...\\\\\\\\n- Didier presents the new version of the data analytics solution PikesPeak - https://pikespeak.ai/ \\\\\\\\n- Jutsu adds IntelliSense, Live Collaboration, Copilot about to land. - https://jutsu.ai\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n----------\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n### [Community Call] #1: Oct 6th, 2023\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**MODERATOR :** Maxwell S\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**VIDEO :** [Tools Community Group Call #1 \\\\u{2013} NEAR DevHub October 6th, 2023](https://youtu.be/vg9LYGLU7ok)\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**AGENDA**\\\\\\\\n-  SourceScan presents the product and upcoming work\\\\\\\\n- Michael (Pagoda) presents bos-loader and workflow\\\\\\\\n- Guillermo presents BOS VSCode extension\\\\\\\\n- Elliot (DevHub) presents some of his toolchain/workflow for building BOS apps\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n----------\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n### [Working Group Call] - January 19, 2023\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**MODERATOR :** Vlad Frolov\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**VIDEO :** [Tooling Working Group Call - January 19, 2023](https://youtu.be/poVmblmc3L4)\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**AGENDA**\\\\\\\\n-   Update on Developer Governance and the NEP process\\\\\\\\n-   Introductions\\\\\\\\n-   Discussion: NEP-418 Proposal to allow attached_deposit in view contexts\\\\\\\\n-   Voting Decision\\\\\\\\n-   Getting Involved\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**NOTES**\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**- NEP-418 :** A proposal to implement an `attached_deposit` host function for view-function calls, so it would just return zero instead of aborting the function call. \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**VOTE DECISION**\\\\\\\\n-   NEP-418 : Approved\\\\\\\\n    \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**ACTION ITEMS**\\\\\\\\n- No action items were discussed\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**RELATED RESOURCES**\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n- NEP-418 Proposal to allow attached_deposit in view contexts - [LINK](https://github.com/near/NEPs/pull/418)\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n[Previous Meeting Notes](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1DGMpaS_X1MSoRae5R0ULClc5Dsv6KmWvfjicFZTJZ64)\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n---------\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n  \\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"textAlign\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"left\\\\\\\"}", "display_name": "Community Calls / Events \\\\u{1f4fa}"}}
